In the MATTER OF Jeffrey D. MARKS, an Attorney at Law (Attorney No. 039501987) D-5 September Term 2018
081896 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 13, 2019

ORDER

This matter having been duly presented to the Court on the petition of respondent, Jeffrey D. Marks, for review of the decision of the Disciplinary Review Board in DRB 18-120, and good cause appearing;

It is ORDERED that the petition for review is denied.
